py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/0/6/06DAC9A6051AE36894977D368193AE4D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Red</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/1/5147ADDB5C5818F28EB0B128F4E43D7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Yellow Gold</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Translucent Purple</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Translucent Red</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Navy Blue</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Metallic Gold</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Natural</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Translucent/Clear</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Soft Pink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Lime Green</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/2/F2BEE86A7A4157D19DCF118993AE2677.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Blue</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Metallic Silver</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Forest Green</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/C/B/CB45D41B879717AA5350FFF0A979F9D8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Maroon</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/4/3448CA74E7277FF40BDF061C2678A47D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Hot Pink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Light Blue</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — 16 oz. Full Color Stadium Cup. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">PPS16-E</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>15 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">500</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}